---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Saktimat: Understand yourself, one day at a time"
  description="A daily check-in companion for people who think differently. Notice your patterns without judgment, shame, or pressure to perform."
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-24 pb-20 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-semibold text-[#1A1A2E] leading-tight tracking-tight mb-6">
      A space to understand yourself,<br class="hidden sm:block" /> one day at a time
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-[#3D4259]/80 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
      Saktimat is a daily check-in companion built for people who think differently, helping you notice your patterns without judgment, shame, or pressure to perform. After noticing your patterns, Saktimat acts as a behavioural operating system, helping you carry that awareness into how you actually live each day.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
      <a
        href="https://app.saktimat.com"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="bg-[#4A90D9] text-white font-medium px-7 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-[#3a7bc8] transition-colors"
      >
        Get Started →
      </a>
      <a
        href="/how-it-works"
        class="text-[#3D4259] underline-offset-4 hover:underline transition-colors"
      >
        See how it works
      </a>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm text-[#3D4259]/60 mt-6">
      Currently in closed beta. Email <a href="mailto:admin@saktimat.com" class="text-[#4A90D9] hover:underline">admin@saktimat.com</a> or call <a href="tel:0435058303" class="text-[#4A90D9] hover:underline">0435058303</a> to request access.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Who it's for -->
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 text-center">
    <p class="text-xl text-[#1A1A2E] leading-relaxed font-medium">
      Saktimat is built for anyone who's ever felt out of sync with themselves.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- What it does -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#1A1A2E] mb-3">Morning check-ins</h3>
        <p class="text-[#3D4259]/80 leading-relaxed">
          A few honest questions about how you're starting your day.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#1A1A2E] mb-3">Evening reflection</h3>
        <p class="text-[#3D4259]/80 leading-relaxed">
          A gentle close to the day, and an Alignment Compass that shows where you landed. Not a score, just a signal.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#1A1A2E] mb-3">Patterns over time</h3>
        <p class="text-[#3D4259]/80 leading-relaxed">
          The longer you check in, the clearer your own patterns become. After noticing your patterns, you can manage this as a behavioural operating system, turning insight into something you actually live by, day to day.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Closing CTA -->
  <section class="py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center bg-[#4A90D9]/8 rounded-3xl py-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold text-[#1A1A2E] leading-snug tracking-tight mb-5">
        Your patterns are trying to tell you something
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-[#3D4259]/80 leading-relaxed max-w-xl mx-auto mb-10">
        Saktimat guides you daily, helping you listen, understand, and act on what you learn about yourself, one check-in at a time.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://app.saktimat.com"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="bg-[#4A90D9] text-white font-medium px-7 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-[#3a7bc8] transition-colors inline-block"
      >
        Get Started →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
